---
import Layout from "../layouts/main.astro";
import { getLangFromUrl, getTranslations } from "../lib/i18n";

const lang = getLangFromUrl(Astro.url);
const t = getTranslations(lang);
---

<Layout title={lang === "es" ? "Política de Cookies - Ibero Data" : "Cookie Policy - Ibero Data"}>
  <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto prose prose-slate">
        {lang === "es" ? (
          <>
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-foreground">Política de Cookies</h1>

            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">Última actualización: Enero 2025</p>

            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">
              Esta política explica qué cookies utilizamos en iberodata.es y cómo puedes gestionarlas.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">1. ¿Qué son las Cookies?</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Las cookies son pequeños archivos de texto que los sitios web almacenan en tu dispositivo. Se utilizan para recordar preferencias, analizar el tráfico y mejorar la experiencia del usuario.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">2. Cookies que Utilizamos</h2>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3 text-foreground">2.1 Cookies Técnicas (Necesarias)</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Son esenciales para el funcionamiento del sitio web. Sin ellas, algunas funcionalidades no estarían disponibles.
            </p>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
              <table class="min-w-full border border-border">
                <thead class="bg-muted">
                  <tr>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Cookie</th>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Finalidad</th>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Duración</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-muted-foreground">
                  <tr>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">lang</td>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">Recordar preferencia de idioma</td>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">1 año</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3 text-foreground">2.2 Cookies de Analítica</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Utilizamos YAAT para entender cómo los visitantes interactúan con nuestro sitio web.
            </p>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
              <table class="min-w-full border border-border">
                <thead class="bg-muted">
                  <tr>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Cookie</th>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Finalidad</th>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Duración</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-muted-foreground">
                  <tr>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">_yaat</td>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">Analítica web anónima</td>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">1 año</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">3. Cómo Gestionar las Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Puedes controlar y eliminar cookies a través de la configuración de tu navegador:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-muted-foreground mb-6 space-y-2">
              <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Google Chrome</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/es/kb/habilitar-y-deshabilitar-cookies" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Mozilla Firefox</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/es-es/guide/safari/sfri11471/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Safari</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/es-es/microsoft-edge/eliminar-cookies-en-microsoft-edge" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Microsoft Edge</a></li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Ten en cuenta que deshabilitar cookies puede afectar la funcionalidad del sitio.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">4. Cookies de Terceros</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Nuestro sitio puede incluir contenido de terceros (como enlaces a redes sociales) que pueden establecer sus propias cookies. No tenemos control sobre estas cookies de terceros.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">5. Actualizaciones</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Esta política puede actualizarse periódicamente. Te recomendamos revisarla regularmente para estar informado sobre el uso de cookies.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">6. Más Información</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Para más información sobre cookies, puedes visitar <a href="https://www.aboutcookies.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">www.aboutcookies.org</a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Si tienes preguntas sobre nuestra política de cookies, contacta con nosotros en <a href="mailto:info@iberodata.es" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">info@iberodata.es</a>
            </p>

            <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
              <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">← Volver al inicio</a>
            </div>
          </>
        ) : (
          <>
            <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-foreground">Cookie Policy</h1>

            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">Last updated: January 2025</p>

            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-6">
              This policy explains what cookies we use on iberodata.es and how you can manage them.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">1. What Are Cookies?</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Cookies are small text files that websites store on your device. They are used to remember preferences, analyze traffic, and improve user experience.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">2. Cookies We Use</h2>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3 text-foreground">2.1 Technical Cookies (Necessary)</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              These are essential for the website to function. Without them, some functionalities would not be available.
            </p>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
              <table class="min-w-full border border-border">
                <thead class="bg-muted">
                  <tr>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Cookie</th>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Purpose</th>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Duration</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-muted-foreground">
                  <tr>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">lang</td>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">Remember language preference</td>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">1 year</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3 text-foreground">2.2 Analytics Cookies</h3>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              We use YAAT to understand how visitors interact with our website.
            </p>
            <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-6">
              <table class="min-w-full border border-border">
                <thead class="bg-muted">
                  <tr>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Cookie</th>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Purpose</th>
                    <th class="px-4 py-2 text-left text-foreground border-b border-border">Duration</th>
                  </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody class="text-muted-foreground">
                  <tr>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">_yaat</td>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">Anonymous web analytics</td>
                    <td class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border">1 year</td>
                  </tr>
                </tbody>
              </table>
            </div>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">3. How to Manage Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              You can control and delete cookies through your browser settings:
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 text-muted-foreground mb-6 space-y-2">
              <li><a href="https://support.google.com/chrome/answer/95647" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Google Chrome</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/enable-and-disable-cookies" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Mozilla Firefox</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://support.apple.com/guide/safari/manage-cookies-sfri11471/mac" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Safari</a></li>
              <li><a href="https://support.microsoft.com/en-us/microsoft-edge/delete-cookies" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">Microsoft Edge</a></li>
            </ul>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Please note that disabling cookies may affect site functionality.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">4. Third-Party Cookies</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              Our site may include third-party content (such as social media links) that may set their own cookies. We have no control over these third-party cookies.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">5. Updates</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              This policy may be updated periodically. We recommend reviewing it regularly to stay informed about cookie usage.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-foreground">6. More Information</h2>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              For more information about cookies, you can visit <a href="https://www.aboutcookies.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">www.aboutcookies.org</a>
            </p>
            <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-4">
              If you have questions about our cookie policy, contact us at <a href="mailto:info@iberodata.es" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80">info@iberodata.es</a>
            </p>

            <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
              <a href="/" class="text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors">← Back to home</a>
            </div>
          </>
        )}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
